<Layout
  title="SMS Terms & Conditions | Regain Hope Detox and Recovery Center"
  description="SMS/text messaging terms for Regain Hope Detox and Recovery Center: opt-in, message frequency, STOP/HELP, and privacy."
>
  <section class="minihero"><div class="container">
    <span class="eyebrow">Messaging</span>
    <h1>SMS Terms &amp; Conditions</h1>
  </div></section>

  <section><div class="container rich" style="max-width:820px;">
    <p>By opting in, you agree to receive SMS/text messages from <b>Regain Hope Detox and Recovery Center, Inc.</b> related to your treatment, admissions, scheduling, or other authorized communications.</p>
    <ul>
      <li><b>Message frequency</b> varies, up to about 4–6 messages per week.</li>
      <li><b>Message and data rates may apply</b>, depending on your mobile carrier and plan.</li>
      <li>Reply <b>STOP</b> at any time to opt out, or <b>HELP</b> for assistance.</li>
      <li><b>Consent to receive SMS messages is not a condition</b> of treatment, admission, or purchase of services.</li>
      <li>Your SMS opt-in consent and phone number <b>will not be shared, sold, or disclosed</b> to third parties or affiliates for marketing purposes.</li>
    </ul>
    <p>For questions about these terms, contact us at <a href="mailto:info@regainhopedetox.com">info@regainhopedetox.com</a> or call <a href="tel:+18182644388">(818) 264-4388</a>. See also our <a href="/privacy/">Privacy Policy</a>.</p>
    <p style="color:var(--muted);font-size:14px;">Regain Hope Detox and Recovery Center, Inc. · 1134 N. Lima St., Burbank, CA 91505</p>
  </div></section>
</Layout>
